  <title>Boroughs and Census Areas</title>
  <abstract>&lt;DIV STYLE="text-align:Left;">&lt;DIV>&lt;DIV>&lt;P>&lt;SPAN>Census Areas 2016 Includes 2010 census data, also includes updated Petersburg Borough Boundary and Wade Hampton name Change to Kusilvak Census Area.&lt;/SPAN>&lt;/P>&lt;P>&lt;SPAN>As of July 2021 adopted as master Feature Class of ongoing rework to get a comprehensive State boundary set for these entities. Census data fields deleted at this time as they are available elsewhere&lt;/SPAN>&lt;/P>&lt;P>&lt;SPAN>As of Nov 2022 New FC name and attributes names to reflect better usage - New in GISS CDO as Borough_Census_Area Master - originally in GISP CDO only as Community Boroughs&lt;/SPAN>&lt;/P>&lt;P>&lt;SPAN>Designed to replace legacy FCs:&lt;/SPAN>&lt;SPAN>GISS CDO Boro_CensusAreas&lt;/SPAN>&lt;SPAN>GISS CDO Community_Master_Boroughs&lt;/SPAN>&lt;SPAN>GISS CDO Community_Master_BoroughsCensusAreas&lt;/SPAN>&lt;/P>&lt;P>&lt;SPAN />&lt;/P>&lt;P>&lt;SPAN>Though technically boundaries of Census Areas are maintained by US Census - but if Alaska DCRA Local Boundary Commission Borough boundaries are adjusted - they impact adjacent Census Areas.&lt;/SPAN>&lt;/P>&lt;/DIV>&lt;/DIV>&lt;/DIV></abstract>
